Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.73,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,わくわくもんだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.73,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,心动不已啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.64,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,わくわくもんモフ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.64,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:53.82,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,本当に機械仕掛けじゃないのよね あなたのぬいぐるみ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:53.82,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,你的布娃娃 真的没有什么机关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.95,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,うん リコちゃんに会うまでは しゃべったことも動いたこともなかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.95,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 在遇到李可前 都没有说过话和动过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.80,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,あ あと あなたじゃなくて みらいね 私
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.80,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,啊 还有别叫“你” 叫我“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.50,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,朝日奈みらい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.50,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,我的名字是朝日奈未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.18,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ中学2年生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.18,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,马上就要升初中二年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.17,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,それ 聞いたから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.17,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,你已经告诉过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.91,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,改めて自己紹介だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.91,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,正式的自我介绍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.69,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,よろしくね リコちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.69,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,请多关照 小李子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.25,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,よろしくモフ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.25,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.08,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,あ うっ ええ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.08,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,呃 好啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.43,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,えっ あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.43,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.80,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,みらい？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.80,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.66,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,どうしたモフ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.66,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.53,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,あっ ごめん 寝落ちしてた？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.53,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 说梦话了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.74,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,初めて魔法界に行くときの夢見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.74,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,我梦到了第一次去魔法界时的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:36.35,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,寝落ちって 冷凍みかん解凍して この数秒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:36.35,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,什么梦话 离解冻冰冻蜜柑才过去几秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.79,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,えっ 本当に？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.79,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.72,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,あれが魔法界よ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.72,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,那里就是魔法界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.88,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,ハァ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.88,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.14,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,わあっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.14,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:15.46,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,久しぶりじゃの みらいくん モフルンくん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:15.46,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,好久不见了 未来 莫夫伦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.97,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,モフ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.97,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,mofu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.28,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,校長先生もおかわりなく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.28,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,校长还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.93,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,校長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.93,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,校长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.68,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,魔法学校の校長先生だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.68,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,他是魔法学校的校长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.46,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,この子が例の
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.46,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,她就是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.48,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.48,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.17,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,リコ先生からの連絡で聞いてはいましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.17,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,虽然已在李可老师的联络中有所听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.87,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,似ていますね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.87,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,但她们可真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.02,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,ああ 確かに ことはくんを思わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.02,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,是的 能让人联想到言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.98,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,ことはってそんなにそっくり？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.98,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,我跟言叶很像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.72,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,うん 髪の色は違えど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.72,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 就头发颜色不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:44.54,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,この髪とっても素敵だよね ひすい色でさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:44.54,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,这头发很棒呢 是翡翠色的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.92,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,ひすい？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.92,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,翡翠？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.59,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,モフ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.59,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,mofu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.46,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,これじゃ モフルンが鬼モフ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.46,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,这样下去 莫夫伦要一直当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.17,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,遅い つまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.17,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,好慢啊 没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:08.73,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,14時間と4分後に 怪物を生み出した者が現れると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:08.73,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,14小时4分后 放出怪物的人就会出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.10,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,はい そう言ってました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.10,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,是的 他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.43,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,その発言があってから 5時間ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.43,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,距离他发言 才过去5小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.07,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,再び彼が現れるまで...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.07,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,他再次出现还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.18,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,えっと...あと8時間モフ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.18,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,呃...还有8小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.56,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,9時間よ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.56,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,是9小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:27.64,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,惜しい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:27.64,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.68,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,モ モフ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.68,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,mo mofu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.72,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,という事は 現れる時刻は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.72,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,那会出现在几时几分呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.46,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,えっと...モフ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.46,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,呃...mofu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.87,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,深夜1時4分ですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.87,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,是深夜1点4分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.41,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,今 言おうと思ったモフ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.41,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,你不说 我也知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:45.48,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,とにかく調べねばな その男のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:45.48,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,总之 先调查那个男人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.17,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,そして あの子のことも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.17,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,还有 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.59,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,みらいくんとリコ先生は彼女といてあげなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.59,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,未来和李可老师 请你们陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.44,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,一緒にいて欲しいというのが彼女の願いならば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.44,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,她是说过 想要跟你们在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.57,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.57,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.47,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,はーちゃんそっくり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.47,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,跟小哈一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.66,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,親戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.66,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,亲戚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.41,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,まあ そんな感じなのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.41,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,应该算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.93,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,ジュンが魔法界に帰ってるなんてね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.93,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,俊回魔法界了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:19.16,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,ナシマホウ界でデザインの勉強しつつ 偶にフランソワさんを手伝ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:19.16,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,我还在无魔界学习服装设计 偶尔会来给法兰西斯师傅帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:23.22,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,ジュンがデザインしたお洋服は大人気なの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:23.22,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,俊设计的服装 可受欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.69,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,みらいちゃんの魔法ガールの制服も最高でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.69,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,未来的魔法少女制服 感觉也很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.26,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,もうワクワクもんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.26,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,真的让我心动不已啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.01,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,あれ作ったのジュンとフランソアさんなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.01,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,做那套衣服的是俊和法兰西斯师傅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:37.34,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,魔法学校の生徒以外は制服着ちゃいけないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:37.34,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,不是魔法学校的学生 不能穿魔法少女制服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.55,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,先生みたく固いこと言うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.55,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,别说这种像老师一样古板的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.66,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,てか 私 先生だし！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.66,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,我就是老师啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.95,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっと大きいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.95,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,有点大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.73,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,だから制服ダメだって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.73,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,都说了不能穿制服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.25,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,キュアップ・ラパパ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.25,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fn法Q喵鸣体}CURE UP·RAPAPA !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.97,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,リボンをチョキチョキ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.97,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,蝴蝶结 咔嚓咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.74,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,おっ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.74,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.04,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,はー 可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.04,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,哈 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.85,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,これならピッタリよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.85,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,这个就跟你很搭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.97,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,私が着けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.97,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,我来帮你戴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:13.58,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:13.58,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.30,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,わあっ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.30,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.02,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,気に入った？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.02,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.64,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.64,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.24,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,お名前 聞いてなかったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.24,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,还没有问你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:26.88,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:26.88,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.56,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,名前？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.56,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.37,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,あ...名前は その
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.37,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,啊...名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:36.59,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,ひすい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:36.59,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.29,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,え...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.29,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,诶...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.06,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,へー ひすいか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.06,Default_CN,,0,0,0,,哦 叫翡翠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.96,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,いい名前だね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.96,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,好名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.22,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.22,Magical_CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.02,Mofurun_JP,,0,0,0,,モフ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.02,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,mofu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.10,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,ひすい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.10,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,翡翠
